,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:00:15.000Z","msg":"用usdt btc 都唔需要用你 係人都整到隻coin"},{"pid":"12b94c2f2d2aa7bedafb9820e63266670d8a81dd","tid":1553512,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c1799b6770322c8d4bd7dac2974f275e90e0c0","tid":1553512,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Mv8Yga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Mv8Yga.jpg&h=3c556e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/STAKE-107886023907915/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSTAKE-107886023907915%2F&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=7ee27c55\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/STAKE-107886023907915/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港正處於危急關頭，前線一直都需要<span style=\"color: red;\">真正的抗爭裝備及消耗品。</span><br />\n<br />\n但是至今的眾籌，不是無助於前線就是騙人的。幾千萬甚至上億的善款，前線幾乎體會不到。<br />\n<br />\n為此我們一班瞭解加密貨幣的人，在此提供一個匿名的集資渠道，此渠道籍ETH（以太幣）募資，並成立<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">加密貨幣STAKE</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n所得ETH（以太幣）將交由某前線物資團隊管理及分配，如果此事成功，才會公開此管理團體的資訊，資金將用作<span style=\"color: red;\">民軍訓練／民軍軍備購入</span>／保釋拘留人士/聘請律師團隊／支持前線義士對抗黑社會勢力／對抗一黨專政／迫使政府滿足五大訴求／懸紅通緝濫權黑警／懸紅內部人士公開CCTV等...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kt1sunV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKt1sunV.jpg&h=deb6cee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSTAKE token將以ICO形式發放，市民只要把ETH（以太幣）發送至地址<br />\n<br />\n<em>(0x9d5fa9654a9409209d5f86c0b6a68227895bc7d7)</em><br />\n<br />\n則相應數量的STAKE token將立刻回送至發送者的以太錢包。<br />\n<br />\n備註：（開始的兌換匯率將是1ETH/999Stake，結束時的兌換匯率將是1ETH/9Stake）<br />\n<br />\nSTAKE成立目的有3大目標：<br />\n1) 解決前線示威者的燃眉之急 （基本溫飽、<span style=\"color: red;\">真正裝備</span>及短期醫療費用）<br />\n2) 使STAKE擁有其支撐價值<br />\n3) 使STAKE能夠充當「積分」（你懂的）用途，在香港各處良心小店流通，我們亦嘗試將之上線到交易所，增加其流通性。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭指出年青一代 have no STAKE of HongKong, maybe you are right, but we are the future and you are not.<br />\n<br />\n這是STAKE名字的起源。<br />\n<br />\n有任何疑問或求助請 telegram : yunghk / k1r1t00<br />\n<br />\n希望佢哋唔會太快搵到我，就算我被自殺，仍會有此基金的繼承人繼續協助各位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQmoM9L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQmoM9L.jpg&h=95d4ffa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSTAKE，真正資助前線的加密貨幣😇<br />\n<br />\n*此貨幣由素人發起<br />\n**你地既錢絕對會去到前線<br />\n***請你明白紅字既意義<br />\n<br />\n----<br />\n註: 呢個lihkg acc係公廁, 有咩搵返文中tg既人, 請勿見怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"701bf7350a8d08e86aa355e25290f0bdbd493fcd","tid":1553512,"uid":117896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:01:16.000Z","msg":"已經同樓主入左1億個幣 又可以賺錢又幫到義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係win win"},{"pid":"185aa90ed447e0ad759f2566d858d4a674ac9357","tid":1553512,"uid":33274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:01:54.000Z","msg":"睇下先"},{"pid":"9364c8c88bf0ae7b1d4afb542b9230f6c51ee955","tid":1553512,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:04:17.000Z","msg":"係就去前線講啦<br />\n唔係唔敢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想賺錢都唔身體力行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3770b06f5d356b2a7b17bc43a23f52f90a11f3d3","tid":1553512,"uid":12417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"收皮啦食人血饅頭"}]}